Masanin, Tiffany Ng daga Jami'ar Michigan, ya lura cewa shi ne farkon carillon na duniya wanda wani dan wasan baƙar fata, Dionisio A. Lind, ya yi wasa a kan, wanda ya ci gaba zuwa babbar carillon na Riverside Church shekaru 18 da suka gabata.
A cewar Merriweather, St. Martin's bai taɓa maye gurbinsa ba.
Abin da ya faru a St. Martin's a cikin watanni biyu na ƙarshe shine rikici tsakanin gine-gine da masu sana'a, waɗanda wasu suka shiga cikin jagorancin coci da wasu na bispedum.
Hukumar da ke kula da Ikilisiyar Ikilisiya, wadda ta ƙunshi mutane masu aikin yi, ta rubuta wa bishop a watan Yuli game da damuwar da ta yi game da yadda bishop ya yi ƙoƙarin tilasta wa cocin ya kashe kuɗi, duk da cewa ba a shigar da gine-ginen ko masu aikin da bishop ya aika ba.
