Shark rauni goma sha uku da haihuwa a kan lobster duck a California
Wani shark ya kai hari kuma ya raunana wani yaro mai shekaru 13 lokacin da ya zo neman hummer a California a ranar Asabar, ranar farko ta kakar hummer, a cewar hukumomi.
An kai harin ne a lokacin da ya kai ƙarfe 7:00 na dare a kusa da Beacon's Beach a Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya gaya wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa ya yi ruwa tare da abokai a kusan rabin sa'a na Asabar da safe lokacin da ya ji yaron yana kuka don taimako, kuma shi da wasu mutane sun yi iyo don su fitar da yaron daga cikin ruwa.
A cewar Hammel, da farko ya yi tunanin cewa yaron ya yi ihu da farin ciki game da kama wani lobster, amma ya fahimci cewa yaron ya yi ihu 'Na yi ciwo!
Na yi ya cije!'
Dukkanin kafaɗarsa sun karye, in ji Hammel, wanda ya gano cutar lokacin da ya kai ga saurayin.
Na yi kira ga kowa ya fita daga cikin ruwan, 'Akwai wani shark a cikin ruwa,' in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron da motar motsa jiki zuwa asibitin Rady Children's a San Diego, inda aka ba shi a cikin yanayin da ya dace.
Ba a san irin shark da ya kai harin ba.
Wani mai kula da gidan wanka, Larry Giles, ya ce a wani taron manema labarai an ga wani shark a yankin makonni biyu da suka gabata, amma an tabbatar da cewa ba wani shark mai haɗari ba ne.
Giles ya kuma ce wanda ya yi hakan ya yi mummunan rauni a cikin babban jikinsa.
Hukumomi sun rufe bakin teku daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas na tsawon awanni 48 don bincike da dalilai na tsaro.
An lura cewa akwai nau'in sharks fiye da 135 a yankin, amma yawancin ba a yi amfani da su a matsayin masu haɗari ba.
Sainsbury's na shirin yin amfani da kasuwar 'yan mata masu kyau a Burtaniya
Sainsbury's yana ƙalubalanci Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams tare da kayan ado na kayan ado da kayan ado masu kyau, waɗanda ke da ma'aikata masu horo.
Ana gwada ɗakunan da aka faɗaɗa a shaguna 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar a matsayin wani ɓangare na babban shigowa cikin kasuwar kayan ado na Burtaniya miliyan 2.8, wanda ke fuskantar ci gaba yayin da tallace-tallace na tufafi da kayan gida ke raguwa. Idan gwajin ya kasance mai nasara, za a faɗaɗa ra'ayin zuwa ƙarin shaguna a shekara mai zuwa.
Ana yin zuba jari a cikin kula da kyau sakamakon ƙoƙarin supermarket na gano sabon amfani da wuri don wuri wanda aka yi amfani da shi a baya don TV-s, microwave ovens da gidaje.
Sainsbury's ta ce za su ninka yawan kayayyakin kula da kyau da suke bayarwa zuwa kayayyaki 3,000, ciki har da alamomi kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw, waɗanda shagon ba su taɓa sayar da su ba.
Samfurori da aka samu daga L'Oreal, Maybelline, da Burt's Bees za su sami wuri mafi kyau a cikin wuraren da aka lura, kamar yadda suke a shagunan kamar Boots.
Har ila yau, Supermarket chain yana sake ƙaddamar da alamar kasuwancin ta ta Boutique tare da kayan cin ganyayyaki, saboda yana samun ƙaruwa a cikin buƙatun wannan tsakanin matasa abokan ciniki.
Bugu da ƙari, mai sayar da turare mai suna The Fragrance Shop zai gwada teburin sayar da kayayyaki a shagunan Sainsbury guda biyu, wanda ya buɗe a Croydon a kudancin London a makon da ya gabata, yayin da ɗayan ya buɗe a Selly Oak a Birmingham a ƙarshen wannan shekara.
Kasuwancin intanet da kuma sabon salo na sayen abinci a kowace rana daga shagunan sayar da kayayyaki na gida yana nufin cewa manyan kasuwanni suna bukatar su yi karin abubuwa don su sa abokan ciniki su zo.
Mike Coupe, darektan gudanarwa na Sainsbury's ya ce, tallace-tallace a hankali za su zama kamar wani kantin sayar da kayayyaki, yayin da supermarket ke yin gwagwarmaya da ƙananan kantin sayar da kayayyaki Aldi da Lidl tare da ƙarin ayyuka da kayayyaki ba tare da abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ta sanya Argos-sayarwa a daruruwan shaguna, kuma ta kuma gabatar da jerin Habitat-sayarwa bayan sayen sarƙoƙi biyu a baya.
Ƙoƙarin da aka yi a baya na Supermarket na inganta sassan kula da kyawawan halaye da kayan magani ya kasa.
Sainsbury's ta gwada wani aiki tare da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma an dakatar da aikin bayan wata gardama game da rarraba kudaden shiga daga kantunan magani a cikin manyan kasuwanni.
Sabon dabarar ta zo ne bayan da Sainsbury's ta sayar da kantunan sayar da kantuna 281 ga Celesio, mai mallakar kamfanin Lloyds Pharmacy, a kan GBP 125 miliyan shekaru uku da suka wuce.
A cewarsu, Lloyds za ta shiga cikin shirin, ta hanyar ƙara wani zaɓi na Luxushud-pleiemarks, ciki har da La Roche-Posay da Vichy, a cikin shaguna hudu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury, ya ce: "Mun canja yanayin da kuma tsarin kayan ado na masu kyau don mu samar da yanayi mai kyau ga abokan cinikinmu.
Mun kuma saka hannun jari a cikin ma'aikata da aka horar da su sosai, waɗanda za su kasance a shirye su ba da shawara da taimako.
An tsara mu don mu cika duk bukatunmu, kuma yanayinmu da kuma wurarenmu na aiki sun sa mu zama masu gasa na yin ado da ke wakiltar sabon kasuwancin kasuwanci.
