Ragowar guguwar Rosa za ta haifar da ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yammacin Amurka
Kamar yadda aka ruwaito, guguwar Rosa ta yi rauni yayin da ta motsa a kan teku mai sanyi a arewacin tekun Mexico.
Duk da haka, Rosa za ta kawo ruwan sama a kan tafiyarta ta arewacin Mexico da kudu maso yammacin Amurka a cikin kwanaki na gaba.
Rosa yana da iska mai ƙarfi na 135 km / h kuma yana da hadari na Category 1 a ranar Lahadi 05.00 ET, yana da nisan kilomita 620 kudu maso yammacin Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
Ana tsammanin cewa Rosa za ta motsa arewa a ranar Lahadi.
A lokaci guda kuma, wani jirgin ya fara kafawa a cikin Pacific Ocean kuma ya motsa zuwa gabas zuwa gabar yamma ta Amurka.
Rosa zai haifar da ruwan sama har zuwa 25 cm a wasu sassan Mexico a ranar Litinin.
Daga nan, hulɗar da ke tsakanin yanayin zafi na tropical da kuma yanayin da ke kusa da shi zai haifar da ruwan sama mai yawa a kudu maso yamma a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
A cikin gida, ruwan sama mai tsayi daga 3 zuwa 10 cm zai haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai haɗari, rushewar ruwa da saurin ƙasa a cikin hamada.
Dyptropic zafi zai haifar da yawan ruwan sama na har zuwa 57 cm a kowace awa a wasu yankuna, musamman yankunan kudu na Nevada da Arizona.
Ana sa ran ruwan sama mai tsawon 510 cm a wasu sassan kudu maso yammacin ƙasar, musamman a kan manyan sassan Arizona.
Akwai yiwuwar ambaliyar ruwa da ta yi saurin tsanantawa saboda ruwan sama na wurare masu zafi.
Ba shi da kyau a yi tafiya a cikin hamada a ƙafa idan dai akwai haɗari ga ruwan sama na tropical.
Ruwa mai ƙarfi zai iya haifar da raƙuman ruwa da ke cikin koguna masu saurin sauka, kuma guguwa za ta haifar da iska ta iska ta gida wanda zai iya ƙunsar ƙura da yashi.
Saurin da ke gabatowa zai haifar da ruwan sama mai ƙarfi na gida don sassan gabar teku a kudu maso California.
Yawan ruwan sama sama sama da 1.3 cm yana yiwuwa, kuma wannan zai iya haifar da rusk mai gudana da sauri, da kuma guntuwar hanyar.
Wannan ne ruwan sama na farko da za a yi a yankin.
Wasu yankunan ruwan sama na wurare masu zafi za su fara kusantar Arizona a ƙarshen ranar Lahadi da yamma da kuma farkon Litinin da safe, kafin ruwan sama ya bazu daga baya a ranar Litinin da Talata.
Za a yi ruwan sama mai ƙarfi a ranar Talata a kan kusurwoyin ƙasar kuma zai ci gaba a ranar Laraba.
Oktoba na iya haifar da wasu matsanancin yanayin zafi a duk faɗin Amurka yayin da Arctic ke da sanyi amma tropes suna da zafi sosai.
Wani lokaci wannan yana haifar da canje-canje masu tsanani a yanayin zafi a kan gajerun hanyoyi.
Za mu ga misali mai kyau na bambancin zafin jiki a tsakiyar Amurka a ranar Lahadi.
Za a samu kusan digiri 11 na bambancin zafin jiki tsakanin Kansas City, Missouri, da Omaha, Nebraska, da kuma tsakanin St. Louis da Des Moines, Iowa.
A cikin kwanaki biyu masu zuwa, zafin bazara na ci gaba zai yi ƙoƙari ya gina kansa kuma ya sake faɗaɗa kansa.
Yawancin sassan tsakiyar Amurka da gabashin Amurka za su fara farawa a watan Oktoba, tare da digiri a kan yawan adadin daga yankin Southern Plains zuwa sassan arewa maso gabashin Amurka.
New York City zai iya kaiwa digiri 26.5 a ranar Talata  wannan zai zama kimanin digiri 5.5 sama da matsakaici.
Rahotonmu na dogon lokaci na nuna cewa gabas ta Amurka za ta yi zafi fiye da yadda ake so a farkon watan Oktoba.
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka halarci taron da aka yi da Brett Kavanaugh
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 da suka kalli gidan talabijin guda shida sun ga shaidar da babban jami'in kotun Brett Kavanaugh da Christine Blasey Ford suka bayar a ranar Alhamis, matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ta yi a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da rikice-rikice na siyasa, kuma masu watsa shirye-shiryen sun katse watsa shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullun don sanar da babban abin mamaki na ranar Juma'a a cikin dakika na ƙarshe, lokacin da ya bayyana cewa sanatan Arizona, Jeff Flake, ya shirya shi don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ya gaya wa majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata da cewa wani mashaya Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta a wani taron makaranta.
A wata shaidar da ya yi da sha'awarsa, Kavanaugh ya nace cewa ya tabbata cewa ba a taɓa yin hakan ba.
Wataƙila an ga sakon a ranar Juma'a fiye da miliyan 20,4 da Nielsen ta ba da rahoton.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin yawan masu kallo don CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a ba da damar samun lambar ba ga sauran hanyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna sauraron, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da matsala wajen auna masu duba ofis.
Don ba da ɗan hangen nesa, wannan lambar kallo ce da ta dace da wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin kwallon kafa ta Amurka ko kuma Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu sauraronsa suka goyi bayan Kavanaugh da babbar sha'awa, ya jagoranci cibiyar sadarwa, tare da matsakaicin yawan masu kallo miliyan 5.69 don sauraron yau da kullun, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ta biyu ne da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3,1, NBC tana da miliyan 2,94, MSNBC tana da miliyan 2,89 kuma CCNN tana da miliyan 2,52, a cewar Nielsen.
Har yanzu suna da sha'awa sosai bayan sauraron.
Flake shine babban mutum na wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Jumma'a.
A safiyar Jumma'a, kyamarar CNN da CBS ta yi masa fim yayin da yake ƙoƙarin ɗaukar hawa zuwa wani taro a cikin kotun kotu yayin da masu zanga-zangar ke ihu da ihu a kansa.
Ya yi ta kallon ta a cikin minti da dama yayin da ake fitar da shi, yayin da aka watsa labarin kai tsaye a CNN.
