An kashe daruruwan mutane a sakamakon tsunami da kuma girgizar ƙasa a Indonesia, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru
An kashe akalla 384 kuma an janye mutane da yawa zuwa teku ta manyan raƙuman ruwa da suka yi ta rawanin raƙuman ruwa a lokacin da wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka kai ga tsibirin Slawesi na Indonesia, a cewar hukumomi a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a wani biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku na birnin Palu a ranar Juma'a, lokacin da har zuwa mita shida na tsayi na raƙuman ruwa suka yi ta busawa a ƙasar a kusa da faɗuwar rana, suka hallaka duk abin da ke cikin hanyarsu kuma suka fitar da mutane da yawa cikin mutuwar nutsewa.
Tsunamien ya zo a cikin ƙuƙwalwa a kan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.5.
Lokacin da tsunami ya faru a jiya, mutane suna ci gaba da aiki a bakin rairayin bakin teku, ba su gudu ba kuma sun ƙare a matsayin wadanda aka azabtar, in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar kula da rikicin Indonesia (BNBP) a wani taron manema labarai a Jakarta.
Tsunami ba shi kaɗai ba, ya kawo motoci, ƙuƙwalwa da gidaje, ya kai ga dukan abin da ke kan ƙasa, in ji Nugroho, kuma ya ba da damar tsunamin ya motsa a kan teku mai buɗewa a cikin saurin kilomita 800 kafin ya kai ga bakin teku.
Wasu sun hau itatuwa don tserewa daga tsunami kuma sun tsira.
