Yayin da kasar Sin ta kara samun karfin aikin fasaha, Amurka za ta bukaci ta ninka yawan kudaden da ta kashe wajen gudanar da bincike a wannan fannin, in ji Kai Fu Lee, mai saka jari da kuma mai amfani da fasaha ta wucin gadi, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Bayanin da ya yi ya zo ne bayan da wasu sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka gabatar da sanarwar da ta shafi ilimin kere kere, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar fasaha ta yau da kullum.
A shekarar da ta gabata ne kasar Sin ta kaddamar da wani shiri da ke nufin ta zama kasa da kasa a fannin kera fasaha ta wucin gadi nan da shekarar 2030.
"Budget din bincike na fasaha zai zama kyakkyawan farawa tun da sauran ƙasashe suna da nisa a baya na Amurka, kuma muna neman babban ci gaba na gaba", in ji Lee.
Taimakon tattalin arziki na iya ninka yiwuwar cewa babban aikin da ake yi a fannin fasaha zai fito ne daga Amurka, Lee ya bayyana a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito ne daga kamfanin Houghton Mifflin Harcourt a wannan watan, shi ne darektan Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera fasaha a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarun 1980 ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon don haɓaka tsarin fasaha na fasaha wanda ya buga mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Othello na Amurka, kuma daga baya ya kasance jagora a Microsoft Research ko darektan sashen Sinawa na Google.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amirka, kamar ta Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a gudanar da gasar gaba, don taimakawa wajen gano masu basira na gaba.
Masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki sosai don karɓar tallafin gwamnati, a cewar Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke satar shugabannin ilimi ba, kamfanoni ne ke sata", in ji Lee.
Facebook da Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan jami'ai don yin aiki da fasaha a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce canje-canje a cikin manufofin baƙi na iya taimaka wa Amurka ta ƙarfafa ƙoƙarinta a cikin ilimin fasaha.
