LeBron zai fara wasan Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Lokaci ya yi kusa da fans da suke son ganin LeBron James yana wasa a Los Angeles Lakers a karon farko.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan a ranar Lahadi a wasan bude gasar gabanin kakar wasa da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Har yanzu ba a yanke shawarar tsawon minti da zai yi wasa ba.
Walton ya ce a shafin yanar gizon Lakers, "Za a yi fiye da ɗaya kuma a kasa da 48".
Dan jaridar Lakers Mike Trundell ya rubuta a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai iya buga takamaiman adadin minti.
Bayan wani motsa jiki a baya a wannan makon, an tambayi James abin da shirin da yake da shi don Lakers 'shekaru shida kafin kakar wasa.
"Ba na bukatar gwagwarmayar farko a wannan mataki na rayuwata", in ji shi.
Lokaci na taron jama'a na Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban ya fara taron jama'a a yammacin yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin taron jama'a biyar da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da wuraren da zai tsaya a garuruwan da ya samu goyon baya sosai, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka yi wa zaben tabbatar da dan takararsa a kotun koli da aka zaɓa jiransa, Trump yana da burin samun goyon baya ga zaɓen na gaba, tun da 'yan Republican suna cikin haɗarin rasa iko akan majalisa lokacin da masu jefa kuri'a suka je zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron jama'ar West Virginia na Trump zai faru a yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya ganinsa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, ya fara ne da misalin karfe 19.00 na yammacin wannan shekara, Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba na shekara ta 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron jama'ar Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron da ake yi a mako na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da cin zarafin jima'i. An sa ran za a yi zaben tabbatarwa har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Babban manufar duk waɗannan taron jama'a shine tallafawa 'yan majalisa masu mulkin mallaka da ke fuskantar babban zaɓe a watan Nuwamba.
Shugaba Trump ya ce, a cikin makonni masu zuwa, za a yi taron jama'a biyar da za su yi don su yi wa masu ba da agaji da masu goyon baya wa'azi, yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin kare da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa tana da muhimmanci sosai ga tsarinsa na siyasa da shugaban kasa zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke fuskantar babban lokacin yakin neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya gaya wa Reuters.
Taron jama'a na yammacin, wanda a cewar shirin zai faru a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, zai iya jawo hankalin 'yan wasan tallafi daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma Pittsburgh-pressen ya rufe shi, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, wani jihar da ya lashe da fiye da kashi 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya yi nisa a zaben.
"Wannan alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba shi ƙarin ƙarfi a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, wani masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA ta nuna halin yaki don riƙe bangaskiya yayin da suka shiga wasan wasan ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman guda uku, za a iya yin taron a ranar Asabar da yamma a kan abin da ake bukata a gasar Ryder Cup na wannan shekara.
Tsarin motsi na motsi yana da cikakkiyar ra'ayi game da wasanni, amma duk da haka wani abu da 'yan wasan suka gaskata, musamman a gasar kamar wannan.
Kuma ina suke ganin wannan ya yi girma?
"Suna da maki shida kuma yanzu suna da hudu, don haka muna da shi tare da mu a matsayin wani momentum", Jordan Spieth ya ce a lokacin da ya bar filin domin rana.
Turai za ta yi nasara da maki hudu kuma za a yi wasa da su 12.
Amma kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, 'yan Amirka sun ji cewa sun sami iska a kan jirgin ruwa kuma suna da dalili mai kyau na samun wahayi, musamman daga Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma dukansu suna da maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya ba da kyawawan wasanni daga tee zuwa green, kuma yana jagorantar misali.
Ƙarƙashin ƙarancin bikin ya karu bayan da ya ci gaba da zagaye, kuma ya koma wani muhimmin matsayi don tayar da wasan zuwa daidaituwa lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu a ƙarƙashin biyu.
