Rangers sun sha wahala a lokacin da Dolly Mengas ta doke Steven Gerrard ta 10 a Livingston.
Ibrox-side so su samu nasara ta farko tun daga Fabrairu nasara 41 a St Johnstone, amma Gary Holt tawagar haddasa Gerrard sauran asarar a kan 18 matches kamar yadda manager da kuma bar baya da takwas maki daga Ladbrokes Premiership-shugabannin Hearts.
