Hiv/aids: China ta ce an samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 a sabon kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da Aids.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka yi fama da cutar a kasar, in ji wakilin lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane kusan dubu 40 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka an yi amfani da su ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji daga baya.
A al'ada, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar yaduwar jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar yanzu ya kusan sifili, in ji wani jami'in kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a kowace shekara, yawan mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane dubu 100.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi watsi da jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana ganin cewa ana nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi.
Saboda ra'ayin da kasar ta nuna game da yadda ake yin jima'i, an yi bincike da ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan suna haifar da rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan yanayin.
Tun shekara ta 2003, hukumomin kasar Sin sun yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a matsayin wani ɓangare na wani shiri don magance matsalar.
