Sanarwar Johnny English Strikes Again  matalauci Rowan Atkinson a cikin ɗan leƙen asiri
Yanzu an zama al'ada don duba abubuwan da suka faru na Brexit a duk sabon fina-finai tare da wani ɗanɗano na Burtaniya kuma yana da alama yana da mahimmanci ga wannan sake farfadowa na parodifranchisen Johnny English actioncomedie wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake tashi a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin, za ku yi ta yin ta'aziyya game da yadda ba mu da bege a yau?
A kowane hali, Johnny English mai rashin cancanta da idanunsa masu kumburi da kuma fuskarsa na roba ya sake samun lasisinsa na yin wannan rooting a karo na biyu.
Yana da wani abu mai ban mamaki, wanda duk da irin wannan James Bond-ambitions, shi ne Mix na Clouseau, Mr Bean da kuma wani ɓangare na mutumin da ke taimakawa tare da guda ɗaya kawai a cikin murya tare da murya mai zafi a lokacin bikin budewa a gasar Olympics a London 2012.
Ya kuma dogara ne da rawar da Atkinson ya taka a cikin tallace-tallace na talabijin da aka manta da su a Barclaycard; mutumin da ke tafiya da kuma na duniya wanda ke barin rikici a ko'ina.
Wannan lokaci ne mai ban mamaki a cikin sabuwar tafiya ta Johnny English.
Na yi farin ciki da yadda Johnny English ya kusanci wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu a cikin kayan aikin tsakiyar zamanai, kuma sai da aka yanke masa kwalkwali.
Atkins yana da baiwa ta wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma yanayin jin dadi yana jin ƙarancin jini da kuma ban mamaki, musamman yanzu da alamun da ke da mahimmanci kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suka ƙi yin wasan kwaikwayo.
Fadawar da ake yi a cikinsa ta fi na yara fiye da manya, kuma a ganina, ba a yi amfani da fades na Johnny English a matsayin mai da hankali da kuma mai da hankali ba kamar na Mr. Bean.
Yanzu dai, abin da ake nufi da hakan shi ne, Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin manyan hanyoyin sadarwar yanar gizo na Birtaniya na 'yan leken asiri kuma ya bayyana asalin dukkan jami'an Birtaniya a fagen, har zuwa mummunan aikin da jami'in tsaro ya yi  wani rawar da Kevin Eldon ya taka.
Wannan shi ne kisa na karshe na firaministan kasar, wani mutum mai girman kai da rashin mutunci wanda ya riga ya shiga cikin cikakken rikicin rashin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson tana aiki mai kyau da wannan rawar Teresa May, amma rubutun ba ta da yawa da za ta yi aiki da ita.
Masu ba da shawara na sirri sun sanar da ita cewa tun da aka gano kowane ɗan leƙen asiri mai aiki, dole ne ta ɗauke wani daga cikin masu ritaya.
Wannan yana nufin Johnny English, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin a wani gidan da ake kira Snob, amma yana koyar da ilimi a asirce. Akwai wasu abubuwa masu kyau a nan, lokacin da English ke ba da makarantar ƙwallon ƙafa ta ƙwallon ƙafa don aikin leken asiri.
An dawo da English zuwa Whitehall don saurin daidaitawa kuma an sake haɗa shi da tsohonsa, mai taimakawa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya buga.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, ya yi wasa da wani mai aiki a jirgin ruwa, wani babban matsayi na musamman wanda Vicki Pepperdine ya yi watsi da shi.
Don haka Batman da Robin suna yin duk abin da suke so a madadin sarauniya, suna fuskantar Olga Kurylenko, babban matar aure, Ophelia Bulletova.
A lokaci guda, firaministan ya yi wa mai fasaha mai ƙwarewa ya yaudare shi, wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin yanar gizo na Birtaniya: Jason Volta, Jake Lacy.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya tare da farseaklike gefe-fage: saka su a matsayin masu hidima suna sanya wuta a wani gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai cin abinci. Suna haifar da rikici yayin da suke ɓoye kansu a cikin jirgin ruwan Luxus yacht na Volta; kuma English ya haifar da tsarkakakkiyar rikici yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da wani VR-kayan aiki don ya san kansa a gidan Volta.
Duk wuraren da aka dakatar da su a zahiri an cire su kafin wasan karshe, amma duk da haka da yadda kyakkyawa da kuma hayaniya yana da haka akwai abubuwa da yawa da ke tunatar da yara TV tare da dukan abu.
Kusan matsakaici, duk.
Kuma kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, ban iya yin komai ba sai na yi tunani: shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson wani rawar da zai iya amfani da baiwarsa?
