Menene bikin Global Citizen, kuma shin ya taimaka wajen magance talauci?
A wannan Asabar, New York ta ba da kyautar bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na shekara-shekara da ke nuna jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da za su yi aiki a duniya.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda yanzu yake shekara ta bakwai, zai sa dubban mutane su yi ta yawo zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, ba wai kawai don ganin irin girman da Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes suka yi ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da talauci mai tsanani ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekara ta 2012, ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan magance talauci ta hanyar sa mutane da yawa su yi aiki don magance talauci.
