"Wannan ya zama tushen farin ciki ga jam'iyyar 'yan jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban RNC (Republican National Committee), a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai game da zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma amincewar karshe ko kuma Kavanaugh ya shiga aiki, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan jam'iyyar Republican suka bi da wannan kuma yadda suka bi da ita", Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiya da ke inganta zaɓen 'yan takara na dimokiradiyya, ya nuna wa tashar labarai.
