Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet don kalubalanci Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, ya kaddamar da wani shiri na farko da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da aka yi a baya na kamfanin, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da ke ci gaba da gina tushen tushen tushen Berners-Lee Solid.
A Solid, masu amfani za su iya zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su iya samun damar yin amfani da su.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azi cewa manufar ita ce mulkin duniya.
Ya ce dole ne mu yi hakan yanzu.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don barin mutane su ƙirƙiri nasu kalar ajiyar bayanai ta kan layi ko POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike guda a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da banbanci game da ajiyar bayanan sirri ta kan layi shi ne cewa yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani wanda zai sami damar yin amfani da irin wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "bayar da kai ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce, kamfanin ya ba da albarkatu, tsari da kuma dacewa da ikon yin Solid ga kowa.
A yanzu haka, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi wa kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma wasu masu shirye-shirye masu son kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu ci gaba da fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na musamman ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook da Google game da ko su gabatar da wani sabon abu ko a'a, wanda zai sa a sake kiran tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
Ba mu nemi izininku ba.
A wani rubutu da aka wallafa a shafin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da ke taimakawa wajen kare mutuncin da kuma ingancin sabon cibiyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance babban murya a cikin muhawara game da rashin daidaito.
Ko da yake ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee har yanzu shine wanda ya kafa kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
