Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne aka kashe a wani girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani da tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu na ƙasar Indoneshiya a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jami'an gwamnati, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutuwar za su ƙaru.
Harkokin sadarwa ba su da aiki, kuma masu ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga Donggala regentskap ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da episenter na girgizar ƙasa da ƙarfin 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palu bayan da aka yi hatsarin.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi, wanda ke cikin ƙarshen wani bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ke gudana a cikin kilomita 300 na iyakar tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regentskap, wani yanki na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin matakin lardin, yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Fishing da kuma aikin gona sune yankunan da ke cikin tattalin arzikin Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Nikkel-gruvedrift yana da mahimmanci a cikin lardin, amma yana da mahimmanci a Morowali, a bakin tekun a gefen Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, tsunami ya mamaye Palu da Donggala, a cewar hukumar kula da ayyukan gaggawa ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kuma kai ga yammacin Donggala a 1996 kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan Yankin da ke cikin Tekun Tsakiyar da kuma girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya kai kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, sama da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yammacin yankin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a wajen tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 6.8 ya afkawa kudu da Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia kuma ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya buge gabar kudu.
2009: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.6 a kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West-Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1100.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.5 ya afkawa ɗaya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, kuma ya haifar da tsunami mai kaiwa mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh kuma ya haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da aka tuna da mutane game da herjing na girgizar ƙasa mai mutuwa da tsunami a shekara ta 2004.
