Hukumomin kara na tarayya sun yi rare neman hukuncin kisa ga wani da ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Hukumomin hukuma na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas  wani mummunan hukunci wanda ba a yi ba a jihar saboda laifin tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe 'yan bindiga da masu bin keke a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don yin hukunci a kan hukuncin kisa, dole ne a tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas forsetly kuma ya haifar da mummunan rauni na jiki tare da niyya, bisa ga sanarwar da aka ba da don neman hukuncin kisa a Southern District of New York.
Duk waɗannan maki biyu sun cancanci hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar shaidar.
Makonni da yawa bayan harin, babban juri na tarayya ya jefa hukuncin kisa na 22 da aka yi a gaban Saipov, wanda ya yi amfani da shi a matsayin hukuma ta tarayya a cikin harkokin aikata laifuka da kuma aikata laifuka da kuma lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci tsare-tsare da niyya, in ji wani mai ba da labari, wanda ya bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi hakan a matsayin mai tsanani, mai tsanani da kuma lalata.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da lalacewar mutum, dukiya da asarar dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, ya bayyana sanarwar game da niyyar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance masu yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun lokacin da Kananan Hukumomin Kudancin New York suka yi wani abu da zai iya ba da hukuncin kisa.
An yanke masa hukuncin kisa a kan laifin kashe 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
A baya an yi kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York, a 1953 ne ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an hukunta su don yin ta'addanci don yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin yakin basasa shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg-ma'aurata a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, daga Uzbekistan, bai nuna wani nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun shari'a.
