Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya bayyana kansa ba laifi ba bayan da ya yi magana a kan 22 maki.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin masu kare Saipov da aka naɗa a hukumance, ya ce sun yi baƙin ciki sosai game da shawarar da hukumar ta yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawara na neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar karbar karba da rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai kara wa duk wanda ya shiga cikin wannan lamarin raunin da ya faru", in ji Patton.
A baya, ƙungiyar tsaro ta Saipov ta nemi hukumomin hukuma su ƙi neman hukuncin kisa.
