Rahoton da aka fitar daga hukumar kula da kifi da dabbobi ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar yawan adadin ruwan sama a yankunan Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton ɓarnawar fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County  wanda ke nuna raguwar ƙarancin taro.
Fitar da fure na algae na ja yana gudana kimanin kilomita 210 a gefen tekun, daga arewa a Pinellas zuwa kudu a cikin Lee County.
An gano tabo a kusan kilomita 16 a wajen tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Redalger a Pasco County.
An bayar da rahoton manyan taro na matsakaici a ko a waje da gabar tekun Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a wajen gabar tekun Hillsborough County, na halitta zuwa manyan taro a Manatee County, na halitta zuwa manyan taro a ko a wajen gabar Sarasota County, na halitta zuwa matsakaici taro a Charlotte County, na halitta zuwa manyan taro a ko a wajen gabar tekun Lee County da ƙananan taro a Collier County.
Har yanzu ana ba da rahoton rashin jin daɗi a cikin hanyoyin iska na Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier County.
Ba a ba da rahoton tashin hankali a cikin hanyoyin iska a arewa maso yammacin Florida a cikin makon da ya gabata ba.
